{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01HBUJ454q59fz4ByuSHAUGR","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"### Page\n- Page URL: https://pr-7-timealign-initial-plat.plat.local/\n- Page Title: timealign-initial — a history timeline placement game\n- Console: 2 errors, 0 warnings\n### Snapshot\n```yaml\n- generic [active] [ref=e1]:\n  - banner [ref=e2]:\n    - link \"Timelines Demo\" [ref=e4] [cursor=pointer]:\n      - /url: /\n  - generic [ref=e6]:\n    - generic [ref=e7]: A history timeline placement game\n    - generic [ref=e8]:\n      - link \"API\" [ref=e9] [cursor=pointer]:\n        - /url: /openapi\n      - button \"Sign in\" [ref=e11] [cursor=pointer]\n  - main [ref=e12]:\n    - article [ref=e13]:\n      - complementary \"Catalogue summary\" [ref=e14]:\n        - generic [ref=e15]: timealign-initial\n        - table [ref=e16]:\n          - rowgroup [ref=e17]:\n            - row \"Puzzles 4\" [ref=e18]:\n              - rowheader \"Puzzles\" [ref=e19]\n              - cell \"4\" [ref=e20]\n            - row \"Events 27\" [ref=e21]:\n              - rowheader \"Events\" [ref=e22]\n              - cell \"27\" [ref=e23]\n            - row \"Span 1776–2018\" [ref=e24]:\n              - rowheader \"Span\" [ref=e25]\n              - cell \"1776–2018\" [ref=e26]\n            - row \"Difficulty Easy – Medium – Hard\" [ref=e27]:\n              - rowheader \"Difficulty\" [ref=e28]\n              - cell \"Easy – Medium – Hard\" [ref=e29]\n            - row \"Source Hand-authored, Wikipedia\" [ref=e30]:\n              - rowheader \"Source\" [ref=e31]\n              - cell \"Hand-authored, Wikipedia\" [ref=e32]\n      - paragraph [ref=e33]: You are shown a historical event with its date hidden, and you slot it onto a shared timeline — before, after, or between the events already placed. Commit to reveal the real date, score the guess, and read more on Wikipedia. It is played in the spirit of the board game Timeline.\n      - heading \"How to play\" [level=2] [ref=e34]\n      - list [ref=e35]:\n        - listitem [ref=e36]: Pick a puzzle from the table below.\n        - listitem [ref=e37]: The board opens with one anchor event already placed and dated. Earlier events sit toward the top, later events toward the bottom.\n        - listitem [ref=e38]: You are handed the rest one at a time, date hidden. Tap a marked gap, then tap Commit.\n        - listitem [ref=e39]: Commit reveals the date. Correct earns 100 points plus a 25-point streak bonus per consecutive hit; wrong scores nothing and snaps into place. Either way the timeline stays in order.\n      - heading \"Puzzles\" [level=2] [ref=e40]\n      - table [ref=e41]:\n        - rowgroup [ref=e42]:\n          - row \"Puzzle Difficulty Events Years\" [ref=e43]:\n            - columnheader \"Puzzle\" [ref=e44]\n            - columnheader \"Difficulty\" [ref=e45]\n            - columnheader \"Events\" [ref=e46]\n            - columnheader \"Years\" [ref=e47]\n        - rowgroup [ref=e48]:\n          - row \"Turning Points in World History Easy 7 1776–2007\" [ref=e49]:\n            - cell \"Turning Points in World History\" [ref=e50]:\n              - link \"Turning Points in World History\" [ref=e51] [cursor=pointer]:\n                - /url: /play/world-history\n            - cell \"Easy\" [ref=e52]\n            - cell \"7\" [ref=e53]\n            - cell \"1776–2007\" [ref=e54]\n          - row \"The Space Race Medium 7 1957–2018\" [ref=e55]:\n            - cell \"The Space Race\" [ref=e56]:\n              - link \"The Space Race\" [ref=e57] [cursor=pointer]:\n                - /url: /play/space-race\n            - cell \"Medium\" [ref=e58]\n            - cell \"7\" [ref=e59]\n            - cell \"1957–2018\" [ref=e60]\n          - row \"Landmark Music Releases Medium 7 1956–2014\" [ref=e61]:\n            - cell \"Landmark Music Releases\" [ref=e62]:\n              - link \"Landmark Music Releases\" [ref=e63] [cursor=pointer]:\n              